---
title: Chorizo, Corn & Courgette Risoni with Parmesan
description: There are plenty of choices for a good risoni out there, but we’re positive we have the winning combination of
ingredients that will top the lot. The mild spice of the chorizo is cooled by a roasted pumpkin, then zested with lemon
juice and doused in a tomato sauce. That sounds (and tastes) like the best to us.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-corn-courgette-risoni-0d60f5e4.jpg
